Description:
    Resize a window in the UIB.  
    
Input Parameters:
    <None>

Output Parameters:
   <None>

Author:  Wm.T.Wood

Date Created: July 1995

Modified: 08-14-2012  Rkamboj  -- Added support for PDS to send height and width of window
  
